snippet.textDisplay: I wasn’t impressed by Bachanal. We ate there last week and I was so disappointed. Lots of selection, but quality and taste weren’t there. Service was horrendous and we are Caesars Diamond (they give you a special “Diamond” flag for your table.) took server ten minutes to make first contact, disappeared for long stretches where we couldn’t find any server. Brought out utensils to break crab shells when we were already finished with our crab.
